MBOMBELA &#8211; Eight suspects held up the iStore in i&#8217;Langa Mall this morning. Nobody was harmed during this incident.Two of the suspects were recognised by staff members, one wearing grey jacket with a man bag and one with an orange hat with jeans.Please be on the lookout for a black BMW 320i, fairly new model and a Grey Volkswagen Golf 7 that were used as getaway vehicles, possibly heading towards White River.If you have any information, please contact 0861 911 677.Lowvelder will update you with more information as it becomes available